text: Family () is a 2001 Dutch drama movie directed by Willem van de Sande Bakhuyzen and was based on the play by Maria Goos. It stars Petra Laseur, Marisa van Eyle, Bram van der Vlugt, Anneke Bok, Mark Rietman. ==Other websites== * Category:2001 drama movies Category:Dutch drama movies Category:Movies based on plays Category:Movies directed by Willem van de Sande Bakhuyzen
title: Family (2001 Dutch movie)
